title: Cedar Cabin style Home on Lake Serene
posting_body: There are two separate residences on this Lake Serene property.
The larger or main residence with spacious living area and full view windows with french doors open to a large solid surface deck over looking the Lake and a garden area.
Home features vaulted ceilings, fireplace, master bedroom w/walk-in closet, second bedroom and bath in lower area.
Range and new Refrigerator in kitchen with washer/dryer in separate laundry area included.
Access to garden, lake, dock, canoe and paddle boards available.
Carport and space for second vehicle if needed.
Looking for tenant/tenants who will be a good fit for this well cared for home.
Not suitable for dogs as there is no fenced yard.
